freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: Intense skin itching near injection site without rash or swelling

Itching still around perimeter of injection site, about 1 inch lower and more to the inner aspect of my deltoid muscle. Slight soreness to touch but have continued to use cold packs to calm the itching and 25 mg of Benadryl at bedtime
